What is this True Atheism thing?  Is there a False Atheism?  True atheism is the non-belief in any god or gods.  This is the aggregation of rejecting individual gods.  So specifically, your god doesn't exist, and neither does his, or hers, or that guy in the back, or any of them.  True Atheism is borne out by disproving each god individually as they are presented.  You claim this god, I disprove it; you then claim this other god, I then disprove it; later, rinse, repeat.  Funny thay can't agree on what a soul is but know absolutely what true atheism is.<br>
